buildIpPortViewParameters

private java.lang.String buildIpPortViewParameters(boolean jspInclude)
Just create a String with the parameters for the URL for parameters ip, port, View. the parameters have priority if and specific Ip querry is build the parameters port andt view are ignored, port have more priority than view, then if a port is selected the view is ignored.

Parameters:
jspInclude - is this a URL for a JSP include? if false & used to separate parameters
Returns:
